<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">I can see you've been online looking for business insurance, but I haven’t yet been able to speak with you to provide you with a quote over the phone.</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></font><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Is there a good time for me to try you again?<br></b></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Here at Kingsbridge we offer a complete package of cover that is designed specifically for UK businesses. Our comprehensive package includes&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Public Liability</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Goods and Tools cover</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">, and&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Employers’ Liability</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;(if required).&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>We can also include optional benefits such as:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Hired in Plant cover</b>&nbsp;- Covers you in the instance that plant equipment was damaged or stolen.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Own Plant cover</b>&nbsp;- Covers you in the instance that plant equipment was damaged or stolen.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Contract Works</b>&nbsp;- Covers you against accidental loss, destruction or damage for materials and labour that you've used caused by an unforeseen event in order to restore the project to its status prior to occurrence.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Professional Indemnity</b>&nbsp;- Covers you against the cost of compensating a client for loss caused by negligent services or advice</font></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"></span></p><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">So, I can discuss with you which parts of the policy would be relevant for your business, it would be great to speak over the phone.<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>When would be a good time for me to reach you?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can contact me on<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>01242 808 740</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>